data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3 bd, 2 bth. craftsman style, HistoryMaker home. Built in 2021, this pristine property has been lovingly maintained by its single owner. As you step inside, you'll be immediately impressed by the bright and airy atmosphere that fills the open-concept living spaces. The living room, featuring freshly updated flooring, provides a comfortable and inviting area to relax and entertain. The kitchen offers modern appliances, ample counter space, and an island with extra seating. It seamlessly flows into the eat-in dining area, making meal preparation and serving a breeze. Sliding glass doors in the dining area open up to a private backyard oasis, where you can enjoy the custom built, covered Pergola with a built-in 65 in. flat screen TV perfect for enjoying game nights & BBQ's with friends and family.
**Seller is offering $5000 buyer incentive**Fridge, washer & dryer can be included with acceptable offer.
